Moscow Hosts Second International Education Fair
MOSCOW , February 26 ( Xinhua ) -- The Second Moscow International Fair on Education started Thursday , attracting educational organizations from 16 countries .
The fair , jointly organized by the Russian ministries of culture and education , will exhibit and demonstrate the latest educational procedures and progress Russia has achieved in elementary and middle school education .
During the fair , text books , audio and video aids and materials , and other teaching equipment will be displayed .
Seminars on education will also be conducted .
The fair will end on March 1st .
